 aktuelle gesellschaftliche Entwicklungen haben sie unvermeidlich gemacht.  afunded by Fachbereich Pflege der Berner Fachhochschule, Zentrum Psychiatrische Rehabilitation der Universitären Psychiatrischen Dienste Bern  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aThis eBook is made available Open Access under a CC BY-NC-ND 4.0 license: uhttps://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-nd/4.0 uhttps://www.degruyter.com/dg/page/open-access-policy  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Apr 2022) 4aBevölkerung. 4aCorona-Virus. 4aCovid-19. 4aGesellschaft. 4aLife Sciences. 4aLockdown. 4aMedien. 4aMedizin. 4aMedizinethik. 4aPandemiebekämpfung. 4aPolitik. 4aPsychologie. 4aSoziologie. 4aWirtschaft. 4aWissenschaft. 4aWissenschaftssoziologie. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Sociology / General.2bisacsh  aCovid-19.  aEconomy.  aLife Sciences.  aLockdown.  aMedia.  aMedical Ethics.  aMedicine.  aPandemic Control.  aPolitics.  aPopulation.  aPsychology.  aScience.  aSociety.  aSociology of Science.  aSociology.2 aFachbereich Pflege der Berner Fachhochschule, Zentrum Psychiatrische Rehabilitation der Universitären Psychiatrischen Dienste Bernefunder.4fnd4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/fnd08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus PP Package 2021 Part 2z978311074335708iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2021z9783110753776oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Sociology 2021z9783110753967oZDB-23-DSL40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783839455456zOpen Access7040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783839455456zOpen Access70423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783839455456/original  a978-3-11-074335-7 DG Plus PP Package 2021 Part 2b2021  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-DGGb2021  aZDB-23-DSLb2021  aZDB-23-GOA